Calculated total score for the Self-Administered Comorbidity Questionnaire, including the two open-ended questions
Notes: Sum all yes/no responses on the HEAL Self-Administered Comorbidity Questionnaire (SCQ) . An individual can receive a maximum of 2 points for each medical condition: 1 point for the presence of the problem, another point if he/she receives treatment for it

ElementDescription: Calculated total score for the Self-Administered Comorbidity Questionnaire, including only the items with problem listed
Notes: Sum yes/no responses to questions with a defined problem listed (Questions 1 - 18) on the HEAL Self-Administered Comorbidity Questionnaire (SCQ).
